<p class="block-text">
<b> Overview of task</b>: We ask you to judge fourteen (14) utterances by Debby. To make sure that you are paying attention, we've included utterances that Debby will definitely think are true and some that she will definitely think are false. If you pay attention, you are sure to get them right!

<br>
<br>

<b> Language survey:</b> At the end of the task, we ask you two short questions about your language background. You will be paid no matter what answers you give in this survey (so please answer truthfully).
<br>
<br>
</p>
-------------- ARE YOU WILLING TO PARTICIPATE IN THIS STUDY? ---------

<br>
<br>

By answering the questions below, you are participating in a study being performed by a linguist affiliated with the Department of Linguistics at The Ohio State University. If you have questions about this research, please contact Judith Tonhauser at tonhauser.1@osu.edu. You must be at least 18 years old to participate. 

<br>
<br>

Your participation in this research is voluntary. You may decline to answer any or all of the following questions, without adverse consequences. Your anonymity is assured.

<br>
<br>

If you do not wish to participate in this study, please return the HIT now.

